// Tutorial 7 — Random mode
//
// @mode:random makes the engine pick a rule at random
// when multiple rules exist for the same symbol.
//
// [weight:N] controls the probability (higher = more likely).
//
// Try: click Produce several times — the result changes!

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser
@mode:random

S -> Motif Motif Motif Motif End

Motif -> C4 E4 G4 E4 [weight:40]
Motif -> D4 F4 A4 F4
Motif -> E4 G4 B4 G4 [weight:30]

End -> C4 _ _ _
